title: Ep165 Cabin Fever Crimes
description: This week, the gals indulge in their self-quarantine to bring you tales of isolation gone awry. Topics include coping skills, jogging jerks, an Antarctic mystery, and a rum-fueled ship-show. Support a local brewery or pop open a can of Insight Brewery's Strawberry Old One-Eye, open a freakin' window, and tune in for Cabin Fever Crimes. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
